cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.CV

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on applying optimal control to improve robotic applications, specifically quadrotor control. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper uses a deep neural network to directly map robot states to control actions. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possible category as the paper deals with control systems for quadrotors. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper uses machine learning techniques to improve the performance of quadrotor control. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is less likely but still possible as the paper may involve visual perception for quadrotor control.
